## MoSCoW Prioritization

### Must Have
- User authentication for recruiters and applicants
- Resume upload and storage
- AI-based resume parsing
- Resume relevance scoring
- Recruiter dashboard to view applicants
- Job posting and application workflow

### Should Have
- AI-generated resume summaries
- Resume filtering and sorting options
- Application status tracking for applicants
- Notification system for application updates

### Could Have
- AI-based resume improvement suggestions
- Advanced analytics for recruiters
- Resume comparison between candidates
- Multi-language resume support

### Won’t Have (For Now)
- Video interview analysis
- Integration with external job portals
- Real-time chat between recruiters and applicants
- Mobile application
